chrome excites abnormally may be due to the following reasons:

1. if you see the following error in the black window then it means the chrome version update took place, the chrome driver/drivers need to be updated.

2. In order to update the drivers please visit the website link given below. on before hand check the current chrome browser version by typing "chrome://version" in a fresh chrome browser tab
LINK: https://chromedriver.chromium.org/downloads 

3.now open the link check for the current version you have seen in the chrome tab in the website and click on the link it redirects you to available dowloads.
for windows: one has to select the 32bit windows version zip file. 

4.when the download begins extract the folder and copy the chromedriver.exe
and simply replace the chromedriver with the driver2 folder of the program file.

 
